Sales Monitoring

 To ensure that the sales of the category in different regions and in different classification of Stores
 Constant review of the concepts in the category.
 Constant review of the category in the four regions in order to supplement sales with optimum stock.
 Providing more substitutes for best selling concepts to capture market.
 Constantly reviewing the performance of new articles across the stores.

Stock Management

 Constant reviewing the depth of the articles in stores.
 To increase and decrease the number of stores based on the selling potential.
 Eliminate the slow sellers and defective lines by interesting promotions and price reduction.
 Constantly mark the discontinued lines and pass the information to the store level so as to ensure a faster clearance of the same.
 Maintain an updated sample stock of the current lines with the updated sales record of all articles.
 Continue follow-up of the articles performance, increasing procurement of those with high sales out rate, stopping those slow movers, but immediately replace production, other alternative.

New Stores Opening

 To involve in new stores plan to ensure right space is allocated to the categories.
 To work out the Merchandise Plan for the store.
